        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Mark 9:30",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "), and were approaching the neighborhood of Capernaum. The privacy was connected with the special instruction which he was now giving to his disciples. ",
        "children": []
